---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CTA from '../components/CTA.astro';
import { business } from '../data/business';

---

<BaseLayout
  title="Alerts & Updates | Healthy Paws Animal Hospital"
  description="Stay informed with the latest alerts, updates, and seasonal pet health reminders from Healthy Paws Animal Hospital in Lake in the Hills, IL."
>
  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="bg-hpah-green-light py-16">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl mb-4">Important Update</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Current Alerts -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose">

        <p>
          <strong>To ensure the highest level of patient data accuracy, we have upgraded our prescription protocols.</strong> <strong>Beginning April 1, 2026, your options for medication will be:</strong>
        </p>

        <ul>
          <li><strong>In-Hospital:</strong> Filled on-site.</li>
          <li><strong>Home Delivery:</strong> Processed through our cost-competitive integrated online pharmacy for seamless home delivery.</li>
          <li><strong>Physical Script:</strong> A paper script prepared for pickup (please allow 2 business days for preparation).</li>
        </ul>

        <p>
          As pharmacies have moved to an integrated platform for human medicine, we have seen a significant increase in errors with faxed prescriptions. Upgrading our prescription protocols will allow us to maintain a seamless medical record for your pet and ensure their medications are handled with the direct oversight they deserve.
        </p>

        <p>Thank you for partnering with us in providing the best care for your pets.</p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTA />
</BaseLayout>
